name: Oracles of the Roasted Goose
description: Hailing from the the regions surrounding Kharth’s Daggers, the Oracles of the Roasted Goose are known for cheffin up the good shit. That good good. Yeah. Now finally living a life of leisure as their ‘investments’ grow their wealth beyond imagining, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
